<html>
<head>
  <meta http-equiv="Content-type" content="text/html; charset=utf-8">
  <style type="text/css" media="screen">
    body { padding: 10px; background-color: #f8f8f8; font-family: Tahoma, Verdana, Arial, Sans-Serif; font-size: 0.8em; }
    #content { margin: 0; width: 700px; border: 1px solid #4e979e; background-color: #fff; color: #666; padding: 10px 20px 10px 20px; }
    h2 { color: #4e979e; margin: 0px; padding: 10px 0px; font-size: 1.2em; }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div id="content">
    <h2>Activity Submitted for Approval</h2>
    <p>This e-mail is from the Impact Equality&trade; assessment tool.</p>
    <p>You have received this e-mail as you have been identified as the relevant approver for the Activity: <strong><%=h @user.activity.name -%></strong>.</p>
    <p>The Equalities Team should have already notified you of this. If you are not the relevant approver please contact the Equalities Team.</p>
    <p>This Activity has now been submitted and is waiting for your approval. The link below will take you to the Activity summary page for <%=h @user.activity.name -%>.</p>
    <p><%= link_to @login_url, @login_url %></p>
    <p>Thank you.</p>
  </div>
</body>
</html>